WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:01.400
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.400 --> 00:00:03.768
I just wanted to say we did it.

00:00:04.644 --> 00:00:07.315
Praise the Lord, mission accomplished.

00:00:07.315 --> 00:00:25.167
When we set out to pray for the President back whenever the election was over, the Lord said, 'You must pray him through the inauguration, for there will be many attacks trying to come against him, against his life, and against the inauguration itself.

00:00:25.167 --> 00:00:33.435
' He said this is going to be a time of great intercessory prayer, and that's exactly what we set out to do.

00:00:33.435 --> 00:00:38.777
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, you're going to raise up a million-man and woman prayer army.

00:00:39.114 --> 00:00:48.389
You're going to pray throughout the whole world and change things in politics and things that I'm going to show you as a watchman on the wall.

00:00:48.389 --> 00:00:53.605
' That's exactly what we've set out to do on this channel—to pray to change things.

00:00:53.605 --> 00:00:57.320
That's what we named our church: Prayer Changes Things.

00:00:58.599 --> 00:01:02.822
Prayer Church was taken and Prayer Foundation was there, so we used Prayer Foundation.

00:01:02.822 --> 00:01:06.708
People ask why we use 'Foundation'; it’s because that's what they had in the state of Oklahoma.

00:01:08.102 --> 00:01:12.399
We're excited to call it Prayer Changes Things because that's what we believe here.

00:01:15.205 --> 00:01:18.251
Thank you for joining me in praying.

00:01:18.251 --> 00:01:24.930
I believe our prayers changed a lot of things these last 100 days.

00:01:24.930 --> 00:01:31.307
I don't know how many days that is from November 5th to January 20th, but it's a lot of days.

00:01:31.636 --> 00:01:33.817
God used us, ladies and gentlemen.

00:01:34.622 --> 00:01:50.000
Whenever He gave me this very strong warning about the trucks, the vans, and all the major attacks I saw trying to come upon America, I believe we delayed it, because the trucks didn't disappear.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:52.591
What I saw in the spirit did not just disappear.

00:01:55.087 --> 00:02:04.610
All I know is that when we pray with our whole heart as believers, we have authority over the devil.

00:02:04.993 --> 00:02:11.239
I know beyond a shadow of a doubt that we have that authority because I've seen it work.

00:02:11.239 --> 00:02:15.175
I've seen prayer change things over and over again.

00:02:15.480 --> 00:02:21.100
People get upset and say, 'You should have a little fruit of something.

00:02:21.100 --> 00:02:50.000
' Just because you have a window of time where you protected the President to get him in and it didn't manifest everything I saw, doesn't mean it went away.

00:02:50.000 --> 00:03:05.070
He said this is something that's going to take continual prayer throughout his presidency.

00:03:05.070 --> 00:03:24.230
There are a lot of bad people in our country right now that were let in across those borders.

00:03:24.230 --> 00:03:55.702
Just because you delayed or stopped something for a window does not mean it went away; it just means they have to re-evaluate because we exposed their agenda in the spirit realm and uncovered a plot.

00:03:56.986 --> 00:04:05.342
They may try to reassess and come at a different angle another day.

00:04:05.342 --> 00:04:11.239
You have to be smarter than that.

00:04:11.239 --> 00:04:19.142
When you uncover the enemy's plans, the enemy has to re-strategize.

00:04:19.142 --> 00:04:28.160
So, we pray and ask the Lord what their next plan is.

00:04:30.945 --> 00:04:31.230
The enemy is relentless.

00:04:31.230 --> 00:04:38.989
Our job on this channel is to continue to pray.

00:04:38.989 --> 00:04:53.351
It's amazing that so much of the world listened to that video instantaneously.

00:04:54.066 --> 00:05:28.300
People who are not familiar with the spirit realm and how things work when you pray are going to criticize and say that guy's flaky because they don't understand what God's called a watchman to do.

00:05:28.300 --> 00:06:00.851
A lot of believers say, 'You should have this or have that,' and I say that's why God didn't call you to tell people—because you're too worried about their opinions.

00:06:00.851 --> 00:06:14.599
I'm addressing this because it needs to be said; I'm not going to sweep it under the rug.

00:06:14.599 --> 00:06:29.060
Similar to other prophetic words that have happened in the past, I've told you all I do not believe I'm a prophetic voice.

00:06:29.555 --> 00:06:54.324
Some say I walk in the prophetic, but I believe I'm called to do what the people who mentored me trained me to do.

00:06:54.324 --> 00:07:20.329
Pastors and evangelists have poured into me, and I've listened to prayer teachings from my youth, sitting under intercessory prayer people like Sister Billye Brim and the WWPs.

00:07:20.329 --> 00:07:23.779
We expect to change things.

00:07:32.204 --> 00:07:38.130
The Lord warns, 'Warning, warning, warning; pray, pray, pray,' and we delay or stop them.

00:07:38.130 --> 00:07:48.354
That's what we are called to do on this channel.

00:07:48.354 --> 00:08:02.949
I want to keep driving this in with you all.

00:08:02.949 --> 00:08:31.431
That's what this channel's for, and that's what we will continue to do over the next four years plus.

00:08:35.519 --> 00:08:46.150
It's not just about America; it's going to be about praying over Ukraine and Israel.

00:08:46.150 --> 00:09:00.590
I've seen more stuff, but I've been slow to release it.

00:09:00.590 --> 00:09:43.314
I used to make a video the same day I got something from the Lord, but because the platform has grown so big, I'm taking the time to pray over what He's showing me.

00:09:43.314 --> 00:10:04.607
That is wisdom when you have millions of people following you.

00:10:20.190 --> 00:10:20.918
I had the word about the inauguration because I was praying.

00:10:21.646 --> 00:10:46.662
I asked, 'What are you going to do to stop these trucks and stop them from hurting all these people?

00:10:46.662 --> 00:10:55.420
' Where did the trucks go?

00:10:55.420 --> 00:11:07.390
He said, 'I'm going to bring in a major cold front.

00:11:07.390 --> 00:11:23.502
' I have this all on video; I can document it and show you.

00:11:31.360 --> 00:11:38.240
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I'm going to bring in a major cold front that is unusual.

00:11:38.240 --> 00:11:48.880
It will be so strong that they'll have to take it indoors.

00:11:51.210 --> 00:11:55.160
I will protect the people through the weather.

00:11:55.160 --> 00:12:08.546
It will be so frigid and the winds will be strong—a blast of cold air.

00:12:08.546 --> 00:12:16.680
' He said it to me three times.

00:12:25.300 --> 00:12:25.600
He said it will change the course of what I saw coming.

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:31.040
Just like He said, it happened.

00:12:31.040 --> 00:12:32.871
My wife recorded it.

00:12:32.871 --> 00:12:39.706
She asked, 'Honey, should you tell them?

00:12:39.706 --> 00:12:59.152
' I said I was going to pray over it first, but it didn't give me enough time to make a video.

00:13:01.800 --> 00:13:05.519
People are cold and will not show up.

00:13:07.445 --> 00:13:17.870
In these cities, people are not moving around much because of an unusual cold snap.

00:13:18.860 --> 00:13:25.399
It will be a sustained cold snap, reinforced three times.

00:13:27.840 --> 00:13:34.706
You will see this as it alters the way people move.

00:13:39.270 --> 00:13:40.180
This is very unusual and deep.

00:13:40.180 --> 00:13:56.188
It will flow down into places like Florida, but I see deep purple up north in Ohio—deep purple cold.

00:13:59.630 --> 00:14:05.492
The Lord is doing it to protect the people.

00:14:05.492 --> 00:14:09.240
It's about the inauguration.

00:14:09.240 --> 00:14:23.669
This will start this week and alter the weather to cooperate with the plan.

00:14:23.669 --> 00:14:31.109
People won't come outside when it's really cold.

00:14:31.109 --> 00:14:43.239
Terrorists don't want to do stuff when it's really cold because they're looking for big crowds.

00:14:43.239 --> 00:14:48.755
Our prayers are altering the weather.

00:14:48.755 --> 00:14:54.071
He's working on our behalf.

00:14:54.071 --> 00:15:09.880
I keep seeing it being reinforced, pulling it down, and changing things so people don't want to travel.

00:15:09.880 --> 00:15:13.960
What's coming is to distract and deter.

00:15:13.960 --> 00:15:21.423
The Lord said, 'Call this and pray for Trump.

00:15:21.423 --> 00:15:44.347
' I heard today to pray that the judge's plan to try to convict him on the 10th be foiled in the name of Jesus.

00:15:44.347 --> 00:16:02.795
We say to that foul devil from hell rising up inside this man: you are bound in Jesus' name.

00:16:02.795 --> 00:16:09.613
You will not succeed in this plan.

00:16:09.613 --> 00:16:22.019
We have authority over this demonic spirit, and your plans are coming to naught.

00:16:22.019 --> 00:16:34.119
We call the Supreme Court justices to rise up and defeat this plan.

00:16:34.119 --> 00:16:41.490
These plots are over in the name of Jesus.

00:16:41.910 --> 00:16:53.845
The Supreme Court justices will rule in our favor, and it will happen quickly.

00:16:53.845 --> 00:17:01.466
The weather changed and got really cold; it was a Siberian front.

00:17:01.466 --> 00:17:14.708
From what I understood, it was the coldest it's been in over 40 years.

00:17:14.708 --> 00:17:27.828
We give God all the glory because He can use the weather to change things.

00:17:27.828 --> 00:17:39.925
If the world isn't hearing Him, He can use the elements of nature to protect.

00:17:39.925 --> 00:17:57.870
Look how big our God is, that He would use the weather to protect our President and the people.

00:17:57.870 --> 00:18:14.029
I saw those drones and the trucks, but He made it so cold it would be miserable to go out.

00:18:14.029 --> 00:18:21.000
Then He brought the people into the stadium.

00:18:24.351 --> 00:18:38.806
We interceded for the stadium; I saw that and brought a video out way before they even announced the parade and ceremony would be held there.

00:18:50.440 --> 00:18:50.809
We got that glimpse from some sisters in Australia to warn everybody.

00:18:58.839 --> 00:19:01.648
It's not all about me; other watchmen saw something in advance.

00:19:16.790 --> 00:19:17.039
So we started interceding for the stadium.

00:19:17.475 --> 00:19:21.266
We're never blindsided by the enemy's plans.

00:19:21.266 --> 00:19:33.380
Thank God for communion; we're going to take it today and rejoice.

00:19:33.380 --> 00:19:39.332
If you're a skeptic, stick around.

00:19:39.332 --> 00:19:54.740
We saw in New Orleans—God rest their souls—the attack the Lord showed us in prayer at my flower bed.

00:20:00.488 --> 00:20:06.440
He said there would be attacks in New Orleans, Las Vegas, and Nashville.

00:20:06.440 --> 00:20:17.569
We saw two of them, but we didn't see the one.

00:20:17.569 --> 00:20:26.420
Do you believe the power of prayer changed that one?

00:20:26.420 --> 00:20:32.509
I believe it did.

00:20:32.509 --> 00:20:48.366
I saw many men in Las Vegas; where did those other men go?

00:20:48.366 --> 00:20:55.865
It was a lone wolf.

00:20:56.400 --> 00:21:07.440
The Lord told me you'll see lone wolf attacks.

00:21:07.440 --> 00:21:33.623
Then the Lord showed me the strip again with the Bellagio and the fountains out front and the Eiffel Tower-looking thing.

00:21:33.623 --> 00:21:56.295
He told me to pray for Las Vegas, as we would see another major attack there in the future.

00:21:56.295 --> 00:22:02.900
I see in part and hear in part.

00:22:02.900 --> 00:22:22.880
I see leaves on trees, so I know the attack in Las Vegas is in a warmer climate.

00:22:41.381 --> 00:22:41.919
Is it February, March, or April?

00:22:41.919 --> 00:22:45.259
I don't know.

00:22:45.259 --> 00:22:50.880
He warns us of things to come.

00:22:50.880 --> 00:22:56.457
He said ten major cities with over a thousand men.

00:22:56.457 --> 00:23:08.326
Those men did not disappear; they didn't just pack their bags and go back across the border.

00:23:08.326 --> 00:23:16.679
This has been an ongoing plot for a long time.

00:23:16.679 --> 00:23:23.137
We will continue to stand in the gap and pray for America to wake up.

00:23:23.137 --> 00:23:48.280
President Trump, with this new administration, will find the evil and expose the darkness because I've seen a plague coming still.

00:23:48.280 --> 00:23:57.500
Everybody was freaking out about the Bible thing.

00:23:57.500 --> 00:24:03.027
'Chicken Little, the sky is falling!

00:24:03.027 --> 00:24:09.709
He didn't put his hand on the Bible!

00:24:09.709 --> 00:24:23.520
' I posted that to see where everyone was at, and it was a mixed crowd.

00:24:23.520 --> 00:24:46.600
Bottom line is John Roberts, the Chief Justice who was swearing him in, started before the family could even get Melania up there with the Bible.

00:24:46.600 --> 00:25:00.000
It wasn't Trump being malicious; it was a mistake.

00:25:00.000 --> 00:25:13.134
People might say that's a harbinger, like Jonathan Cahn's harbingers.

00:25:13.134 --> 00:25:16.845
I'm curious what he would say.

00:25:16.845 --> 00:25:24.747
Will President Trump re-swear himself in on the Bible?

00:25:37.411 --> 00:25:46.695
I believe it's a vow to God to lead by His direction for this country as one nation under God.

00:25:55.760 --> 00:25:58.093
I don't think there's a conspiracy behind everything all the time.

00:26:06.896 --> 00:26:07.192
I don't drink the Kool-Aid.

00:26:07.192 --> 00:26:30.314
We can get off into some weird stuff with conspiracy theories and Q stuff, like people saying Trump was president the whole time during Joe Biden's inauguration.

00:26:38.249 --> 00:26:42.267
I don't believe that.

00:26:42.267 --> 00:26:48.768
Let's be balanced and keep our eyes on Jesus.

00:26:48.768 --> 00:26:56.959
I believe Jesus has made us the head and not the tail.

00:26:56.959 --> 00:27:06.200
We're going to go through these four years with victory.

00:27:14.886 --> 00:27:16.914
I feel hope, but I still feel the lingering darkness.

00:27:16.914 --> 00:27:24.120
We still have work to do.

00:27:24.120 --> 00:27:33.537
We're going to ask the Lord to protect our finances.

00:27:34.753 --> 00:27:48.240
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, watch George Soros in the days ahead.

00:27:48.240 --> 00:28:04.327
' I was shown George Soros passing away and his son rising up.

00:28:04.327 --> 00:28:20.799
I saw his son was more of a tyrant than George Soros.

00:28:24.960 --> 00:28:31.693
The Lord said these are the signs to watch.

00:28:31.693 --> 00:28:55.034
I saw Klaus Schwab, the guy over the WHO, being removed, and I saw a darker one coming up behind him.

00:28:56.947 --> 00:29:08.640
I saw George Soros passing away, and the Lord showed me Hitler again.

00:29:08.640 --> 00:29:20.700
He said, 'Brandon, this is an Antichrist spirit that was on Hitler.

00:29:20.700 --> 00:29:29.019
' You are about to see Emmanuel Macron rise up like you wouldn't believe.

00:29:36.973 --> 00:29:38.046
He is going to take an Antichrist role in the days ahead.

00:29:38.046 --> 00:29:43.031
Watch him, for he is an Ishmael before the Isaac.

00:29:43.031 --> 00:29:48.315
The Isaac is coming; he is being groomed.

00:29:48.493 --> 00:29:54.475
I saw demonic spirits grooming a man behind a curtain.

00:30:07.640 --> 00:30:08.194
The church, the ekklesia, the bride, is holding back that Antichrist man right now by our prayer.

00:30:08.194 --> 00:30:18.379
But an Ishmael is rising up, and it's Emmanuel Macron.

00:30:32.347 --> 00:30:32.693
You will see him take great power and make big moves.

00:30:32.693 --> 00:30:39.531
Then you will see the Antichrist spirit that was on Hitler; it's grooming the man behind the curtain right now.

00:30:46.000 --> 00:30:54.459
The Lord spoke to me and said Turkey will become friends with Syria and come to their aid.

00:31:02.680 --> 00:31:06.613
I saw a distressed Syria cowering down, and an Islamic brotherhood coming forth in a strong wave.

00:31:06.613 --> 00:31:15.084
When you see your brother being picked on, you defend them.

00:31:15.084 --> 00:31:25.818
Syria is wounded, and I saw Turkey rising up viciously to defend its brother.

00:31:31.670 --> 00:31:31.980
I saw great blows coming to Iran.

00:31:35.657 --> 00:31:43.071
All the Islamic communities—from Syria to Yemen, Oman, Iraq, and Iran—will try to band together.

00:31:43.832 --> 00:31:51.160
But as Iran is afflicted, people treated them like a 'red-headed stepchild.

00:31:51.160 --> 00:32:00.074
' They didn't treat them with the same brotherhood as Syria.

00:32:06.039 --> 00:32:17.617
I don't understand that vibe, but the Lord showed me that while they defend Iran, they don't really like them.

00:32:18.851 --> 00:32:28.548
You will see Iran, but they won't be treated as well as Syria or Hamas.

00:32:30.128 --> 00:32:36.180
I saw a plan being devised against Israel.

00:32:36.180 --> 00:32:42.080
Another major blow will come against Israel.

00:32:42.080 --> 00:32:50.290
I saw them regrouping and saw Damascus becoming a ruinous heap.

00:32:50.290 --> 00:33:01.005
As Trump comes in, they're going back into their holes to strategize.

00:33:01.005 --> 00:33:17.100
I've warned you about biological weapons coming out of the mountains of Iran into Syria and Damascus.

00:33:17.100 --> 00:33:27.860
I saw 50-gallon drums of a yellow substance—biological barrels.

00:33:27.860 --> 00:33:41.452
I've described this to people in the military, and they said it sounds like Agent Orange.

00:33:41.688 --> 00:33:46.206
This is what I'm praying over.

00:33:51.462 --> 00:34:09.204
I saw Donald Trump rising up, and I know they're going to make Canada and America one currency, and eventually Mexico as they take the Panama Canal.

00:34:09.204 --> 00:34:21.120
I have not seen anything about Greenland, so I cannot add that.

00:34:25.944 --> 00:34:26.300
I only saw Canada.

00:34:26.300 --> 00:34:36.173
I saw Justin Trudeau being removed and replaced by a more conservative person.

00:34:36.173 --> 00:34:47.864
They will have revival from sea to sea, from the Atlantic to the Pacific.

00:34:47.864 --> 00:34:59.800
I have seen a major revival coming throughout the whole world—one last push for a mighty harvest.

00:34:59.800 --> 00:35:10.020
America will rise up, and Donald Trump will put the pieces together.

00:35:10.020 --> 00:35:15.693
People ask about the economy crash.

00:35:15.693 --> 00:35:38.710
In October, the Lord told me that because His people humbled themselves and prayed, He is giving us a four-year window of reprieve.

00:35:38.710 --> 00:35:45.645
He is giving us an opportunity for change.

00:35:59.007 --> 00:36:06.804
It was decided in the courts of heaven to give an extended time of grace for revival and a financial outpouring.

00:36:09.851 --> 00:36:14.899
The wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous.

00:36:14.899 --> 00:36:28.420
You will see a major turn in finances through gold, silver, cryptos, and the Iraqi Dinar.

00:36:30.950 --> 00:36:37.267
This will be the greatest transfer of wealth the world has ever seen.

00:36:37.267 --> 00:37:00.128
I was disappointed about the 'Trump coin' because I didn't hear about it in time, but then it crashed, so maybe that was God's protection.

00:37:01.367 --> 00:37:04.720
I keep my eyes on Jesus.

00:37:04.720 --> 00:37:15.800
Don't worry about what everyone says on the internet.

00:37:15.800 --> 00:37:25.680
I was told that the President's family watches these videos.

00:37:25.680 --> 00:37:30.099
If you're watching, Mr.

00:37:30.099 --> 00:37:32.488
President, we love you and pray for you.

00:37:32.488 --> 00:37:33.975
We are raising a prayer army to protect you.

00:37:33.975 --> 00:37:43.119
God has a plan and purpose for you in these end times.

00:37:43.119 --> 00:37:49.462
We pray for your sons, daughters, and grandkids.

00:37:49.462 --> 00:37:51.380
Thank you for sacrificing your life.

00:37:53.569 --> 00:38:00.220
You released those people from January 6th and you're making America great again.

00:38:02.005 --> 00:38:05.010
Thank you from my family to yours.

00:38:05.530 --> 00:38:06.849
We will always lift you up.

00:38:06.849 --> 00:38:11.480
We've interceded for hundreds of hours.

00:38:11.480 --> 00:38:21.200
So let's take communion as a family and give God glory.

00:38:21.200 --> 00:38:32.295
We wrestle not against flesh and blood, but against principalities and powers.

00:38:32.295 --> 00:38:37.440
We have authority over the devil.

00:38:37.440 --> 00:38:49.319
Father, I thank you for President Trump and the Solomon anointing on his mind.

00:38:51.171 --> 00:38:59.623
You chose a man of character to help us out of this hole.

00:38:59.623 --> 00:39:07.965
Trump isn't the Savior, but he is a covering.

00:39:07.965 --> 00:39:22.863
We got rid of a bad covering, and the enemy is being restrained.

00:39:22.863 --> 00:39:28.720
When the righteous rule, the people rejoice.

00:39:28.720 --> 00:39:35.737
We thank you for the character of this man.

00:39:35.737 --> 00:39:42.501
Keep him in your hand and preserve him.

00:39:42.501 --> 00:39:45.119
Keep him from pride.

00:39:45.119 --> 00:39:48.985
Father, we lift up this body.

00:39:54.684 --> 00:39:54.920
You are the healer.

00:39:54.920 --> 00:39:58.880
We apply the blood of Jesus.

00:39:58.880 --> 00:40:03.554
Forgive this nation for aborting so many babies.

00:40:03.554 --> 00:40:07.890
We repent as a nation.

00:40:07.890 --> 00:40:13.346
I thank you for the states standing against abortion.

00:40:13.346 --> 00:40:25.705
There will be a clear dividing line between those that stand for God and those that don't.

00:40:25.705 --> 00:40:29.315
Seed time and harvest will excel.

00:40:29.315 --> 00:40:34.747
We plead the blood over President Trump, his wife, and children.

00:40:34.747 --> 00:40:41.822
I'm not a Pharisee; I love Jesus with all my heart.

00:40:41.822 --> 00:40:45.515
Thank you for taking this seriously.

00:40:45.515 --> 00:40:52.640
My wife and I pray for every one of you.

00:40:58.060 --> 00:40:58.230
The best is yet to come.

00:41:06.100 --> 00:41:10.529
I believe in 'Secret Service' angels—special ops angels protecting the President, my family, and all of you.

00:41:19.212 --> 00:41:19.519
I talk about Big George—he's real and he's my friend.

00:41:19.519 --> 00:41:26.040
God rebukes the devourer for our sake.

00:41:26.040 --> 00:41:32.510
I have the faith of a mustard seed.

00:41:38.639 --> 00:41:39.280
God is a rewarder of those who diligently seek Him.

00:41:39.280 --> 00:41:45.185
I've had a rough couple of days spiritually.

00:41:50.540 --> 00:42:09.649
The Lord showed me that when you get knocked into a ditch, a Good Samaritan might pull you out, but they aren't necessarily supposed to be in your life forever.

00:42:24.613 --> 00:42:24.884
You bless them and let them pass through.

00:42:24.884 --> 00:42:30.928
Some people are just there for a moment.

00:42:47.662 --> 00:42:47.953
Thank you to all the people who have helped me out of my ditch.

00:42:47.953 --> 00:42:54.234
2025 has been an amazing year so far.

00:42:54.234 --> 00:43:01.090
I've seen storms, but we have a reprieve.

00:43:01.090 --> 00:43:05.720
Breathe in the victory of the inauguration.

00:43:08.119 --> 00:43:09.859
Father, I bless these people.

00:43:10.294 --> 00:43:24.930
We believe 2025 will be the year of babies for those who haven't been able to conceive.

00:43:24.930 --> 00:43:30.510
Everything they put their hands to will prosper.

00:43:33.640 --> 00:43:35.520
This will be a time of acceleration.

00:43:35.520 --> 00:43:41.440
Like President Trump said, we will 'drill, baby, drill.

00:43:41.440 --> 00:43:48.280
' I prophesied that he would say that.

00:43:48.280 --> 00:43:58.775
I thank you for the wealth coming to America—a golden age.

00:43:58.775 --> 00:44:15.028
Klaus Schwab and Emmanuel Macron will not be here much longer, but the Antichrist spirit is still here.

00:44:15.028 --> 00:44:23.499
If you're new here, please like and subscribe.

00:44:23.499 --> 00:44:39.480
We're reaching the lost one soul at a time through our YouTube channels in China, Japan, Korea, and France.

00:44:39.480 --> 00:44:40.380
Jesus loves you so much.

00:44:40.380 --> 00:44:42.964
God bless you all.
